<hymn_number>11214</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - mạlysẖ gẖyrk ydạwyny wysẖfyny wạlạqy rạḥty mʿạh
 mạlysẖ gẖyrk yfrḥny yryḥny wqt ạlsẖdẗ ạlqạh
 (mạlysẖ gẖyrk yṣbrny yqdrny ʿly̱ ṣʿạb ạlḥyạẗ)2
 1- (mạlysẖ gẖyrk wqt ạlẓlm ydạfʿ
 wqt ạlạ̉lm lậhạty sạmʿ )2
 wqt ạlḥrb ạ̹lhy rạyty rạfʿ
 2- (mạlysẖ gẖyrk wqt ạlḥzn yfrḥny
 wqt ạlhm ysẖyl ʿny ʿmrh mạyjrḥny)2
 (yṭyb rwḥy wyrjʿly ạ̉frạḥy
 yṭbṭb ʿlyạ wạlạqy mʿạh ạrtyạḥy)2</lyrics>
<title>mạlysẖ gẖyrk</title>
</song>